<subSubSection id="3EB9F2EDA78885ED91CD12EE57600DA3" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" type="description">
<paragraph id="FD9FD83315861A1F6F464CB1DF13865A" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="53F3663290805422687FEB133995073E" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Shell sub-ovate, laterally compressed, with long, sharply pointed posterior rostrum. Periostracum shiny, medium brown. Posterior rostrum shorter, less defined in juveniles. Voucher specimen NHM_181 shell length 13.5 mm, width 7.6 mm (Fig. 6A).</paragraph>
<caption id="A91575BE8987E1B4302D394AC17A27C9" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
